summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Portal Dosare - Romanian legal case monitoring system. Backend APIs working correctly with SOAP integration to just.ro. Frontend fully functional after fixing Select component issue.

minor_bugs.issue: Returns 200 instead of 401 when Authorization header is empty (should return 401)
minor_bugs.impact: Minor security issue - auth middleware not strict enough

expected_behaviors.behavior: Returns 0 results for test searches - expected since using test data with just.ro SOAP API
expected_behaviors.note: SOAP integration working correctly, just no matching test data

fixed_bugs.issue: SelectItem with empty string value causing React runtime errors
fixed_bugs.fix_applied: Changed empty value to 'all' and updated form handling

passed_tests: Landing page loads with all features and CTA buttons
User login with JWT token authentication
Dashboard shows stats (1 monitored case, 0 notifications, admin role)
Search page - single search form visible and functional
Search page - bulk search textarea visible and functional
Admin users page accessible for admin user
Admin stats page accessible for admin user
Backend API authentication and authorization working
SOAP integration with just.ro API functional
